# Trading Log Analysis and Risk Management\n\nThis agent monitors the trading dashboard at http://localhost:5001/ to perform performance analysis and risk management. It extracts trading logs, status updates, and risk parameters (capital, stop loss, take profit). \n\n## Alerting Mechanism\n\n- **Stop-Loss/Take-Profit Triggered:** If any stop-loss or take-profit levels are hit, an alert will be generated.\n- **Critical Drawdown Indicators:** The agent will monitor for signs of critical drawdown, indicating significant risk.\n\n## Logging\n\n- **Extracted Data:** All extracted data will be logged to `/Users/chetantemkar/.openclaw/workspace/app/trading_monitoring.log`.\n- **Critical Alerts:** Any data deemed critical (due to triggered stop-losses, take-profits, or drawdown indicators) will be saved to `/Users/chetantemkar/.openclaw/workspace/app/critical_alerts.log`.\n\n## Execution\n\nThis monitoring is scheduled to run periodically. The extracted data will be summarized and provided as plain text.\n